Sentencas: Anode substrate has a great effect on screen-printing fabrication of yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) electrolyte film and cell performance.
Titulo: NiO plus YSZ anode substrate for screen-printing fabrication of YSZ electrolyte film in solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: In this work, NiO+YSZ anode substrate was prepared by a conventional ceramic sintering method, on which dense YSZ electrolyte film was successfully fabricated by screen-printing method.
Titulo: NiO plus YSZ anode substrate for screen-printing fabrication of YSZ electrolyte film in solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Microstructure of the anode substrate and cell performance were investigated.
Titulo: NiO plus YSZ anode substrate for screen-printing fabrication of YSZ electrolyte film in solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The optimal amount of addition of starch to the anode substrate was 20wt%.
Titulo: NiO plus YSZ anode substrate for screen-printing fabrication of YSZ electrolyte film in solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The optimal temperature for pre-sintering of NiO powder was 800 degrees C. A single cell with the NiO powder pre-sintered at 800 degrees C exhibited the highest power density of 0.95 W cm(-2) at 700 degrees C. (c) 2008
Titulo: NiO plus YSZ anode substrate for screen-printing fabrication of YSZ electrolyte film in solid oxide fuel cell
